{"tid":2403121,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃色年宵旺場 今最後衝刺","createTime":"2021-02-11T02:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T15:41:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b1102c7b61fe0189b899a44299a97263b466c5ac","tid":2403121,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:17:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210211/M7SKGKE46NAQ3JNZTX5VRFRGJ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210211%2FM7SKGKE46NAQ3JNZTX5VRFRGJ4%2F&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLAjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=4b983b14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210211%2FM7SKGKE46NAQ3JNZTX5VRFRGJ4%2F&h=ca35a646\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210211/M7SKGKE46NAQ3JNZTX5VRFRGJ4/</a><br />\n<br />\n黃色年宵旺場 今最後衝刺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CwwmjNX80DWel5rP6YXEZ89bAj8=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UBBQOWNTYBGQJGEKIHNCACH3YU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCwwmjNX80DWel5rP6YXEZ89bAj8%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUBBQOWNTYBGQJGEKIHNCACH3YU.jpg&h=107327e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■似水牛年行街街年宵市集今會延長開放時間到凌晨1時。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】行年宵是港人農曆新年前傳統，但前年爆發反送中運動，政府「基於安全理由」翌年取消年宵乾貨攤位，今年因疫情再度取消。不過，民間仍自發舉辦多個黃色年宵市集，有負責人表示人流絡繹不絕，部份檔主首日已回本，新春期間會再舉辦市集。商戶表示，希望更多港人趁年卅晚出來消費撐同路人。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：儂友和你散貨 場內搵「初心」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有檔主首日已回本<br />\n<br />\n民間年宵市集遍佈港九新界，大大小小超過12個。在銅鑼灣舉辦「牛宵」的負責人Wing表示，「尤其係（星期）五、六、日好旺，keep住好多人嚟」，部份檔主向她表示首日已回本，「好睇係賣啲咩，木錶、賀年食品好受歡迎，可能啲人覺得木錶設計好特別」，其中一檔售賣陳皮檸檬因售罄已停擺兩日。<br />\n<br />\n為了應付今日人潮，牛宵已增加霧化消毒劑數目，且會控制入場人數，「超過100人要喺門口等一等」，並延長開放時間至凌晨12時。主辦單位由年初二至初七亦會舉行新春市集，將有不同類型攤位。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：黃大仙祠直播 法師代上頭炷香<br />\n<br />\n在荔枝角香港工業中心舉辦「似水牛年行街街年宵市集」負責人TY指，年初做過同類市集，反應踴躍。今次比之前稍遜，「係上次好好，所以今次暫時比上次跌三至四成」。市集內較受歡迎是手工藝品，例如銀包、揮春、利是封等，亦有不少人購食品和書籍。今日亦會延長開放時間到凌晨1時，若人流太多會安排派籌和截人龍。<br />\n<br />\n「HongKong_IN」在牛頭角工廈滙集30黃店舉辦「港嘢2.0之撐&ldquo;喜&rdquo;香港私人市集」，主辦單位會將各檔主扣除成本後的一成盈利捐贈612人道支援基金。活動負責人光仔表示，市集年廿七開始，人流和生意一般，「咁啱撞正呢幾日閒日，啲人要返工，時間上有影響」，加上疫情反覆，希望今日最後一日「唔好太差」，暫時較多人買小飾物、揮春、利是封等。他又指，今日特意設有一個「靠運氣」小遊戲，希望帶給港人驚喜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-kKqCQ9u6oU1A828zE9HzPhWrHE=/889x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5JSCZ45WNFG27BM3RRPRBKFTME.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-kKqCQ9u6oU1A828zE9HzPhWrHE%3D%2F889x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5JSCZ45WNFG27BM3RRPRBKFTME.gif&h=6067b4f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vv4b5xqES1yqFAv4-YwJGWg5H6o=/882x1190/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O5KAQUMNXBGB7CGX7SPTBKLTEY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fvv4b5xqES1yqFAv4-YwJGWg5H6o%3D%2F882x1190%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO5KAQUMNXBGB7CGX7SPTBKLTEY.gif&h=6a424a22&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"323d45999485f20d71e2eaa8af636050fe4f8721","tid":2403121,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:18:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7d5512dab3f437b2d6a12a290b8c84bbdb6a14","tid":2403121,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7c54aa6d81809de391f3b40d8d07c57f06e6bc","